  "name": "prompsit-d3-structured-resource-integrity",
  "description": "D3 - Structured-resource integrity. Real i18n resource fragments (Android string resources, Apache-2.0) in four format profiles (xml/json/properties/arb), EN -> 9 languages, where the resource skeleton (keys, schema) must be preserved and only values translated. Open layer = dev (full references) + test inputs + contrastive pack; test/hidden references withheld. Version 1.0 uses oracle-validated machine labels (oracle_validated); human review is not required.",
  "version": "1.0",
  "datePublished": "2026-06-22",
  "license": "https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/",
  "url": "https://mozilladatacollective.com/",
  "citeAs": "Prompsit D3 - Structured-resource Integrity (v1.0, 2026).",
